      "content": "okay thanks. i have some extra strength ones in the cabinet, like the ones that are 1000mg per dose. is it safe if i just take two of those at once to make sure it works? i really dont want to go to the er if i can avoid it, it's just a lot of money and i'm mostly just uncomfortable.",
